'''戴夫·基斯·史都華'''（{{lang-en|David Keith Stewart}}，{{bd|1957年|2月19日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手。於1975年大聯盟選秀第16輪被道奇隊選走，生涯曾效力過道奇、遊騎兵、費城人、運動家與藍鳥等隊。史都華生涯拿下3次世界大賽冠軍，並曾經連續4季拿下單季20勝。

史都華在退休後曾於教士、釀酒人與藍鳥等隊擔任投手教練，也曾在響尾蛇擔任過總經理，不過他在2016年底遭到開除。
==職業生涯==
===洛杉磯道奇===
1978年9月22日，史都華登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/LAN/LAN197809220.shtml|title=September 22, 1978 San Diego Padres at Los Angeles Dodgers play-by-play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308203311/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/LAN/LAN197809220.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時他後援兩局，被敲出一安與送出一次三振。1979年和1980年，史都華都在3A磨練身手。<ref name=minors>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=stewar002dav|title=Dave Stewart minor league statistics & history|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2015-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322172639/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=stewar002dav|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CS>{{cite web|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/1981/0710/071036.html|title=How the baseball strike hits a rookie pitcher|first=Phil|last=Elderkin|work=Christian Science Monitor|date=July 10, 1981|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227031939/https://www.csmonitor.com/1981/0710/071036.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ARydf2CNxXYC&q=Dave+Stewart+baseball+Albuquerque+Dukes+1978&pg=PA45|title=Baseball in Albuquerque|author=Gary Herron|access-date=September 26, 2014|isbn=9780738579641|year=2011}}</ref>

1981年，史都華受邀參加春訓。由於他沒有選擇權，因此不得再被下放小聯盟。而球隊原本就此打算釋出他，不過最後他們將另一名投手Don Stanhouse釋出。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Iyu5Iu2ZJcIC&q=Dave+Stewart+1982+Dodgers&pg=PA47|title=Rick Monday's Tales from the Dodgers Dugout|first=Rick|last=Monday|access-date=September 26, 2014|isbn=9781582619750|year=2006}}</ref>史都華在該年球季初登板就奪勝，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SFN/SFN198104130.shtml|title=April 13, 1981 Los Angeles Dodgers at San Francisco Giants play-by-play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308154730/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SFN/SFN198104130.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>整年他出賽32場比賽，拿下6次救援成功，防禦率2.49。[[1981年國家聯盟分區賽|1981年國家聯盟分區賽]]，史都華得到了震撼教育，他在前兩場比賽都砸鍋吞敗。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/HOU/HOU198110060.shtml|title=October 6, 1981 National League Division Series Game 1, Dodgers at Astros, play-by-play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309012127/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/HOU/HOU198110060.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/HOU/HOU198110070.shtml|title=October 7, 1981 National League Division Series Game 2, Dodgers at Astros, play-by-play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105053547/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/HOU/HOU198110070.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過道奇隊仍靠著強大的韌性連贏三場淘汰太空人。而他在世界大賽上出賽1場失1分，道奇也以4勝2敗拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1981_WS.shtml|title=1981 World Series (4-2): Los Angeles Dodgers (63-47) over New York Yankees (59-48)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808152127/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1981_WS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1982年，史都華拿下9勝8敗，防禦率3.81。<ref name=BR>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/stewada01.shtml|title=Dave Stewart statistics & history|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303181250/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/stewada01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>球季結束後，球隊一開始打算用史都華向遊騎兵交易捕手Jim Sundberg，不過最後被Sundberg用不得交易條款拒絕。<ref name=Swap>{{cite web|url=http://texas.rangers.mlb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20070913&content_id=2206144&vkey=news_tex&fext=.jsp&c_id=tex|title=Swapping Stories: Dave Stewart trade|work=Texasrangers.com|first=Jamey|last=Newberg|date=September 13, 1985|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225238/http://texas.rangers.mlb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20070913&content_id=2206144&vkey=news_tex&fext=.jsp&c_id=tex|dead-url=no}}</ref>1983年他為道奇隊出賽46場比賽，拿下5勝2敗，防禦率2.96。7月11日，他曾罕見的丟出一次暴投，結果讓壘上三名跑者得分的記錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1983/07/13/sports/plays-3-run-series-of-mistakes-for-dodgers.html|title=PLAYS; 3-Run Series Of Mistakes For Dodgers|first=Sam|last=Golaper|date=July 13, 1983|access-date=September 26, 2014|work=New York Times|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308142814/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/07/13/sports/plays-3-run-series-of-mistakes-for-dodgers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===德州遊騎兵===
1983年8月19日，道奇仍將史都華和一名日後指定球員交易至遊騎兵，換來Rick Honeycutt。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsok.com/joe-klein-rocks-the-boat-baseball-is-shocked-at-honeycutt-trade/article/2036453|title=Joe Klein Rocks the Boat Baseball Is Shocked at Honeycutt Trade|first=Jim|last=Lassiter|date=August 21, 1983|work=newsok.com|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222708/http://newsok.com/joe-klein-rocks-the-boat-baseball-is-shocked-at-honeycutt-trade/article/2036453|dead-url=no}}</ref>1983年球季末，史都華拿下5勝2敗，防禦率2.14。不過他在1984年陷入低潮，開季僅拿下7勝14敗，防禦率4.73。最後他也丟了先發位置。<ref name=BR/><ref name=Swap/>  1985年1月，Tom House加入遊騎兵成為新任投手教練。他看出了史都華的問題，並要求他練習指叉球。<ref name=Swap/>

這年遊騎兵讓史都華擔任後援投手，不過他表現還是很差。5月22日，他在被擊出逆轉3分砲後遭到球迷予以噓聲相待。賽後他不僅說這些球迷都是笨蛋，甚至還挑釁他們要他們上場打球。<ref name=Swap/>最後他被球隊總經理Tom Grieve給罰款5000美元，不過球隊老闆似乎不接受這個裁決，他要求Grieve盡早將史都華交易。<ref name=Swap/>最後他在1985年9月13日被交易至費城人，<ref name=Swap/>這年他在遊騎兵只拿下0勝6敗，防禦率5.42。<ref name=BR/>
===費城費城人===
休賽季期間，史都華曾與日職的讀賣巨人有接觸。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1955&dat=19860123&id=BgMiAAAAIBAJ&pg=3190,1750294|work=Reading Eagle|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=September 24, 2014|title=Reading Eagle - Google News Archive Search}}</ref>不過最後雙方並未簽約，因此他又重返費城人。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1356&dat=19860201&id=SqNPAAAAIBAJ&pg=7016,104131|work=Ocala Star-Banner|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=September 24, 2014|title=Ocala Star-Banner - Google News Archive Search}}</ref>

史都華為費城人出賽次數不多，1985年至1986間只出賽12場比賽，防禦率高達6.00。<ref name=BR/>儘管有消息指出史都華手臂受傷導致球威下滑，不過費城人仍於1986年5月9日將其釋出。<ref name=Swap/>後來史都華提到費城人曾要求他若不惹事生非就會將他交易，但最後卻食言反而將他釋出。<ref name=Sun>{{cite web|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1991-01-12/sports/1991012074_1_baltimore-orioles-orioles-finished-rader|title=A's Stewart once spurned by Orioles Baltimore had shot to sign him in '86|first=Alan|last=Goldstein|date=January 12, 1991|work=Baltimore Sun|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072534/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1991-01-12/sports/1991012074_1_baltimore-orioles-orioles-finished-rader|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===奧克蘭運動家===
史都華原本打算加入金鶯，不過金鶯卻告訴他他連2A都上不了，因此史都華轉而與運動家簽約。<ref name=Sun/>他在運動家3A出賽1場比賽後就登上大聯盟。7月1日，他在與印地安人的比賽中揍了對方總教練一拳，結果造成板凳清空事件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1986-07-02/sports/sp-476_1_dave-stewart|title=Stewart Lands Punch to Manager Corrales, but Indians Knock Out A's, 9-0|work=Los Angeles Times|access-date=September 24, 2014|first=Dan|last=Hafner|date=July 2, 1986|archive-date=2014-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521235156/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-07-02/sports/sp-476_1_dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來他被禁賽四場，且遭到罰款處分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-07-22/sports/8602220913_1_fined-narcotics-officers-tumor|title=Baseball Punishes Two Combatants|first=Michael|last=O'Donnell|work=Chicago Tribune|date=July 22, 1986|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074043/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-07-22/sports/8602220913_1_fined-narcotics-officers-tumor|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在這年也新開發了指叉球，<ref name="JamesNeyer2004">{{cite book|last1=James|first1=Bill|last2=Neyer|first2=Rob|title=The Neyer/James Guide to Pitchers: An Historical Compendium of Pitching, Pitchers, and Pitches|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7FfRLE6I5EEC&pg=GBS.PA394.w.1.3.0|access-date=May 25, 2012|date=June 15, 2004|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn=9780743261586|pages=394–395|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301172257/https://books.google.com/books?id=7FfRLE6I5EEC&pg=GBS.PA394.w.1.3.0|dead-url=no}}</ref>整年投出9勝5敗，防禦率3.74。<ref name=BR/>

隔年，他與球隊簽下2年50萬美元的延長合約。<ref name=Speed>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1987/08/25/sports/stewart-lowers-speed-and-is-rolling-again.html|title=Stewart Lowers Speed And Is Rolling Again|first=Michael|last=Martinez|date=August 25, 1987|work=New York Times|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308151815/https://www.nytimes.com/1987/08/25/sports/stewart-lowers-speed-and-is-rolling-again.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1987年，他拿下單季20勝，防禦率3.68。1988年，他更是開季前8場先發全勝，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1988-07-31/sports/sp-10766_1_pitcher-dave-stewart|title=Baseball Miscellany : Names And Numbers|first=John|last=Weyler|date=July 31, 1988|work=Los Angeles Times|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306031133/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-07-31/sports/sp-10766_1_pitcher-dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/mlb-pitchers-of-the-month.shtml|title=Major League Baseball Pitcher of the Month|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308062524/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/mlb-pitchers-of-the-month.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後他拿下21勝12敗，防禦率3.23。他在美聯冠軍賽先發2場全勝，幫助運動家4連勝橫掃紅襪。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1988_ALCS.shtml|title=1988 ALCS (4-0): Oakland Athletics (104-58) over Boston Red Sox (89-73)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308121425/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1988_ALCS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1988-10-10/sports/sp-2812_1_dave-stewart|title=Stewart Homes In on His Second Chance|first=Mike|last=Downey|work=Los Angeles Times|date=October 10, 1988|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006180003/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-10-10/sports/sp-2812_1_dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而他在世界大賽首戰賽前卻威脅道奇二壘手Steve Sax，他放話會在比賽中讓他受傷。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mIMDhzWGrJgC&q=Dave+STewart+1988+World+Series&pg=PT174|title=World Series Game 1|work=Miracle Men: Hershiser, Gibson and the Improbable 1988 Dodgers|first=Josh|last=Suchon|date=1988|access-date=September 27, 2014|isbn=9781623682200}}</ref>後來這場比賽由道奇隊的Kirk Gibson敲出再見全壘打獲得勝利。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK198810190.shtml|title=October 19, 1988, World Series, Game 4: Dodgers at Athletics|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308142754/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK198810190.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>史都華後來於第四場登板，不過仍吞下敗仗，道奇最終4勝1敗拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1988_WS.shtml|title=1988 World Series (4-1): Los Angeles Dodgers (94-67) over Oakland Athletics (104-58)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2007-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071130235359/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1988_WS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1989年，史都華拿下21勝9敗，防禦率3.32。他不僅被選為明星賽先發投手，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1989-07-11/sports/8907110154_1_reuschel-elected-by-fans-all-star-game|title=Bo Leads Off All-star Surprises|work=Orlando Sentinel|date=July 11, 1989|first=Jerome|last=Holtzman|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2015-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406161306/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1989-07-11/sports/8907110154_1_reuschel-elected-by-fans-all-star-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在賽揚獎票選上還拿下第二名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1989-11-16/sports/sp-2087_1_al-cy-young-award|title=Saberhagen AL Cy Young Award Pick : Baseball: Kansas City pitcher, a two-time winner, is the overwhelming choice of voters. Oakland's Dave Stewart is runner-up.|work=Los Angeles Times|date=November 16, 1989|first=Larry|last=Stewart|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306150147/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-11-16/sports/sp-2087_1_al-cy-young-award|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來他在美聯冠軍賽拿下2勝，防禦率2.81。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1989_ALCS.shtml|title=1989 ALCS (4-1): Oakland Athletics (99-63) over Toronto Blue Jays (89-73)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309043509/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1989_ALCS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>在世界大賽首戰上，他還完封了巨人隊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1989-10-15/sports/sp-352_1_dave-stewart|title=A Consistent Guy : Stewart Continues Impressive Postseason Pitching With Shutout|first=Ross|last=Newhan|work=Los Angeles Times|date=October 15, 1989|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518135453/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-10-15/sports/sp-352_1_dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然中間比賽一度因為大地震而延期，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/espn25/story?page=moments/26|title=26. World Series halted by earthquake|work=ESPN.com|first=Rick|last=Weinberg|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305034451/http://espn.go.com/espn/espn25/story?page=moments%2F26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/2009-10-12-world-series-earthquake_N.htm|title=20 years later, the earthquake that shook the baseball world|first=Jose L.|last=Ortiz|work=USA Today|date=October 14, 2009|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224121933/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/2009-10-12-world-series-earthquake_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過運動家還是以4連勝橫掃巨人奪冠。史都華在系列賽拿下2勝，防禦率1.69，順利奪得世界大賽MVP。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1989_WS.shtml|title=1989 World Series (4-0): Oakland Athletics (99-63) over San Francisco Giants (92-70)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2007-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071130235404/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1989_WS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>球季結束後，他與運動家簽下2年700萬美元的延長合約，一度寫下大聯盟史上最大的合約紀錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=yQwSAAAAIBAJ&pg=3872,4846522&hl=en|title=Stewart is latest to have top pact|work=Gainesville Sun|date=January 18, 1990|access-date=September 27, 2014}}</ref>

1990年，史都華拿下22勝11敗，防禦率2.56。6月29日，他投出了無安打比賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20100804&content_id=13019756&vkey=news_t435&fext=.jsp&sid=t435|title=Thursday! Former MLB star Dave Stewart arrives at 'The Nat'|work=milb.com|first=Rob|last=Fai|date=August 4, 2010|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308065410/http://www.milb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20100804&content_id=13019756&vkey=news_t435&fext=.jsp&sid=t435|dead-url=no}}</ref>道奇隊的[[費南多·瓦倫祖拉|費南多·瓦倫祖拉]]也在同一天投出無安打比賽，形成大聯盟單日出現兩場無安打的空前紀錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/classic/s/moment010629valenzuela-stewart-nohitters.html|title=Valenzuela, Stewart each throw no-hitters|work=ESPN.com|first=Larry|last=Schwartz|date=November 19, 2003|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2016-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720165056/http://espn.go.com/classic/s/moment010629valenzuela-stewart-nohitters.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>史都華在美聯冠軍賽拿下2勝，防禦率僅1.13。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1990_ALCS.shtml|title=1990 ALCS (4-0): Oakland Athletics (103-59) over Boston Red Sox (88-74)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308115816/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1990_ALCS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>運動家不僅連三年闖進世界大賽，史都華也成功拿下聯盟冠軍賽MVP。不過他在世界大賽上卻吞下2敗，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1990/10/17/sports/world-series-one-team-does-dominate-in-game-1-the-reds.html|title=WORLD SERIES; One Team Does Dominate in Game 1: the Reds|first=Joseph|last=Durso|work=New York Times|date=October 17, 1990|access-date=September 27, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308141411/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/10/17/sports/world-series-one-team-does-dominate-in-game-1-the-reds.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>最終運動家遭到紅人橫掃。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK199010200.shtml|title=October 20, 1990 World Series Game 4, Reds at Athletics|access-date=September 27, 2014|work=Baseball Reference|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207224850/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK199010200.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

球季結束後，史都華代表大聯盟明星隊與日本明星隊進行8場的友誼交流賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1990-11-06/sports/sp-4272_1_cecil-fielder|title=U.S. All-Stars Striking Out in Japan : Team Including Cecil Fielder, Dave Stewart Loses 4 Straight|work=LA Times|date=November 6, 1990|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074037/http://articles.latimes.com/1990-11-06/sports/sp-4272_1_cecil-fielder|dead-url=no}}</ref>1991年，他因為肋骨受傷首次進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1991-05-09/sports/sp-1945_1_major-league|title=DAILY REPORT : AROUND THE MAJOR LEAGUES : Stewart Leaves Game, May Miss 2 Starts|date=May 9, 1991|first=Alan|last=Drooz|work=LA Times|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007011850/http://articles.latimes.com/1991-05-09/sports/sp-1945_1_major-league|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他只有拿下11勝11敗，運動家也沒能進入季後賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1991-08-10/sports/sp-294_1_dave-stewart|title=Stewart Is Doing What Comes Naturally|work=LA Times|first=Mike|last=Reilly|date=August 10, 1991|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006171317/http://articles.latimes.com/1991-08-10/sports/sp-294_1_dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1992年，史都華依舊因傷所苦，<ref name=playoffs>{{cite web|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1992-10-07/sports/1992281124_1_la-russa-mark-mcgwire-dave-stewart|title=A's, Jays swap roles for playoffs Ex-Bash Brothers are underdogs|work=Baltimore Sun|first=Peter|last=Schmuck|date=October 7, 1992|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006105623/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1992-10-07/sports/1992281124_1_la-russa-mark-mcgwire-dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他拿下12勝10敗，防禦率3.66。<ref name=BR/>儘管成功重返季後賽，運動家仍以2勝4敗輸給藍鳥，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1992_ALCS.shtml|title=1992 ALCS (4-2): Toronto Blue Jays (96-66) over Oakland Athletics (96-66)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308130624/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1992_ALCS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是運動家的這兩勝都是由史都華所拿下。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199210070.shtml|title=October 7, 1992 ALCS Game 1 Oakland at Toronto|work=baseball reference|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308124949/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199210070.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1992/10/13/sports/on-baseball-keeping-a-promise-stewart-stays-perfect.html|title=ON BASEBALL; Keeping a Promise, Stewart Stays Perfect|first=Claire|last=Smith|date=October 13, 1992|work=New York Times|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310184956/https://www.nytimes.com/1992/10/13/sports/on-baseball-keeping-a-promise-stewart-stays-perfect.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===多倫多藍鳥===
1992年12月8日，史都華與藍鳥隊簽下2年合約。儘管他本人希望能續留運動家，不過他發現藍鳥比運動家更尊重他，因此忍痛決定轉隊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1992-12-09/sports/sp-1558_1_blue-jays|title=BASEBALL WINTER MEETINGS : Cone Returns to the Royals : Meeting: Blue Jays get Stewart for two years, $8.5 million. Mariners keep Griffey Jr. for four years, $24 million.|work=LA Times|first=Maryann|last=Hudson|date=December 9, 1992|access-date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006131513/http://articles.latimes.com/1992-12-09/sports/sp-1558_1_blue-jays|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=respect>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1993-10-23/sports/sp-48903_1_toronto-blue-jays|title=WORLD SERIES / TORONTO BLUE JAYS vs. PHILADELPHIA PHILLIES : More Than a Title Is on the Line : Game 6: For the Blue Jays' Stewart, respect is as important as a third championship ring.|work=LA Times|first=Bob|last=Nightengale|date=October 23, 1993|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006215630/http://articles.latimes.com/1993-10-23/sports/sp-48903_1_toronto-blue-jays|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1993年，他拿下12勝8敗，防禦率4.44。<ref name=BR/>儘管季中他因為大大小小的傷勢導致出賽不穩定，藍鳥依舊給予他機會，最後成功闖進季後賽。<ref name=respect/> The Blue Jays made it to the [[1993_American_League_Championship_Series|ALCS]] where Stewart got the call in game two. He allowed only one run in six innings of work to pick up the win.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA199310060.shtml|title=October 6, 1993 ALCS, Game 2: Toronto at Chicago play by play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308231105/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA199310060.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>史都華在美聯冠軍賽第二場先發，他主投6局失1分奪勝。在他下一次先發的前一天，當他的隊友都飛往芝加哥時，他人卻在多倫多，協助救世軍發送食物給難民。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1993-10-12/sports/1993285110_1_salvation-army-dave-stewart-thanksgiving|title=Eve of game, Stewart warms hearts, not arm|work=Baltimore Sun|first=John|last=Eisenberg|date=October 12, 1993|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006073940/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1993-10-12/sports/1993285110_1_salvation-army-dave-stewart-thanksgiving|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在美聯冠軍賽第6場先發，主投7.1局失2分奪勝。球隊也成功闖進世界大賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA199310120.shtml|title=October 12, 1993 ALCS Game 6, Toronto at Chicago play by play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308172105/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHA/CHA199310120.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也獲選為美聯冠軍賽的MVP。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1993_ALCS.shtml|title=1993 ALCS (4-2): Toronto Blue Jays (95-67) over Chicago White Sox (94-68)|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2011-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110805105916/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1993_ALCS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在世界大賽上，史都華表現難得失常。他在第二場先發吞敗，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199310170.shtml|title=October 17, 1993 World Series, Game 2: Philadelphia at Toronto play by play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129205603/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199310170.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>第六場主投6局失4分。不過最後藍鳥靠著Joe Carter驚天動地的再見3分砲拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199310230.shtml|title=October 23, 1993 World Series, Game 6: Philadelphia at Toronto play by play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193548/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199310230.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1994年，史都華拿下7勝8敗，防禦率5.87。<ref name=BR/>後來這年球季因為罷工而提前結束，史都華後來也表示自己因為那場罷工，導致對棒球的熱情日益消退。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/08/23/sports/sports-of-the-times-stewart-still-in-there-pitching.html|title=Sports of The Times; Stewart Still In There Pitching|work=New York Times|first=Claire|last=Smith|date=August 23, 1994|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309063729/https://www.nytimes.com/1994/08/23/sports/sports-of-the-times-stewart-still-in-there-pitching.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2014/08/11/1994-mlb-strike/13912279/|title=1994 strike most embarrassing moment in MLB history|first=Bob|last=Nightengale|work=USA Today|date=August 11, 2014|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222083614/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2014/08/11/1994-mlb-strike/13912279/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===重返運動家===
在罷工結束後，史都華與運動家簽下1年約。不過他已經無法找回過往身手，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199504260.shtml|title=April 26, 1995 Oakland Athletics at Toronto Blue Jays play by play and box score|work=Baseball Reference|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308135858/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/TOR/TOR199504260.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他僅拿下3勝7敗，防禦率高達6.89。最後總教練只好將他調往牛棚，並讓25歲的投手Todd Van Poppel接替先發位置。<ref name=retires>{{cite web|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1995-07-24/sports/1995205133_1_stewart-returned-haas-wally|title=As man, Stewart will always be an A's ace|work=Baltimore Sun|first=Steve|last=Kettmann|date=July 25, 1995|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006084805/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1995-07-24/sports/1995205133_1_stewart-returned-haas-wally|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而史都華不想再成為牛棚投手，因此他在7月24日公開宣布退休，並說到這是他人生中的最低谷。<ref name=retires/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spokesman.com/stories/1995/jul/24/stewarts-career-as-oaklands-ace-comes-to-an-end/|title=Stewart's Career As Oakland's Ace Comes To An End|work=The Spokesman Review|agency=Associated Press|date=July 25, 1994|access-date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308112701/https://www.spokesman.com/stories/1995/jul/24/stewarts-career-as-oaklands-ace-comes-to-an-end/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==個人生活==
史都華與他的前妻共有2名女兒。<ref name="SI">{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/vault/1989/11/06/120946/a-hero-lives-here-as-ace-dave-stewart-was-the-series-mvp-but-in-oakland-hes-much-more-than-that|title=A HERO LIVES HERE A's ace Dave Stewart was the Series MVP, but in Oakland he's much more than that|first=Peter|last=Gammons|work=Sports Illustrated|date=November 6, 1989|access-date=September 26, 2014|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116101042/https://www.si.com/vault/1989/11/06/120946/a-hero-lives-here-as-ace-dave-stewart-was-the-series-mvp-but-in-oakland-hes-much-more-than-that|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1985年，史都華因為被懷疑與一名妓女發生不雅暴露而遭到逮捕，後來發現這名妓女具有變裝癖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1985-01-25/sports/sp-9423_1_dave-stewart|title=Rangers' Dave Stewart Is Arrested for Lewd Conduct|work=Los Angeles Times|access-date=September 24, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006172647/http://articles.latimes.com/1985-01-25/sports/sp-9423_1_dave-stewart|dead-url=no}}</ref>在不爭辯答辯後，史都華被判處罰款與緩刑。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=861&dat=19850130&id=1K1HAAAAIBAJ&pg=6074,6886355|work=The Victoria Advocate|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=September 24, 2014|title=存档副本|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414020207/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=861&dat=19850130&id=1K1HAAAAIBAJ&pg=6074,6886355}}</ref>兩天後，史都華獲選由達拉斯沃斯堡運動記者選出的好男人獎(Good Man Award)，史都華在獲獎時曾說到他的罪與這個獎都是他人生中的恥辱。<ref name="SI"/>
